<br />\n<br />\n呢兩晚太夜訓 <br />\n一教訓天光<br />\n訓教好似係完全冇問題㗎<br />\n但一醒個人就進入放負狀態"},{"pid":"f7ed091272bfb575000a516902abcfe548f592b1","tid":252393,"uid":113802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T16:00:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>感覺辛苦完一大輪，建立所有野<br />\n到最後都係咩都帶唔走<br />\n最後都係零 唔知有咩意義</blockquote><br />\n咁冇結果 <br />\n都可以有過程嘅<br />\n係咪可以咁諗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"adfdbc1e72d5da1a70b16d923a38a11b6955ec73","tid":252393,"uid":116609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T16:17:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>呢個問題要你自己思考要有意義</blockquote><br />\n諗唔到所以先求教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁首先諗下自己身體狀況適唔適合思考先？<br />\n睡眠質同量如何？<br />\n枕頭合唔合適？<br />\n會唔會太夜瞓？<br />\n有冇得發夢？<br />\netc.</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n呢兩晚太夜訓 <br />\n一教訓天光<br />\n訓教好似係完全冇問題㗎<br />\n但一醒個人就進入放負狀態</blockquote><br />\n一起身就放負，咁即係其實睡眠質素應該唔好得去邊<br />\n如果瞓得好，應該起身時好精神好positive"},{"pid":"deeab4f4107119155828b5bde1d825abf3317ddb","tid":252393,"uid":70760,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T16:21:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"313718affaf331d97a39883ab80cbe68c95b48d5","tid":252393,"uid":23388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T16:28:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>最近個人好似行屍酒肉咁<br />\n朋友唔想搵<br />\n屋企人唔想理<br />\n晚晚都唔想訓教<br />\n好似咩都提唔起精神咁<br />\n生存好似冇咩意義<br />\n可以點算好<br />\n<br />\n純粹上嚟放下負 <br />\n唔該唔好叫我去死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n人為人而活 至於係咩人 你要問你自己"},{"pid":"e8220e9ecfbf93f5b7600696bc284c085a0e1f31","tid":252393,"uid":2507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T16:29:12.000Z","msg":"為咗生存而生存<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d222e8724a2dd759996dc8dfb48a564d2a12788","tid":252393,"uid":113802,"like":